import React from "react";
import { Card, Row,Col } from 'react-bootstrap';
import "../App.css";
import Project from "../components/project"
function Portfolio() {
  return (
      <Row>
      <Col>
<Project 
    img=" https://github.com/mengyue-z/Online-Offline-Budget-Trackers/raw/main/public/images/screenshot1.png"
    title="Budget Tracker"
    description="This is a budget tracker application that users will be able to add expenses and deposits to their budget with or without a connection.
When entering transactions offline, the total will be populated when the application is back online."
    repo="https://sleepy-depths-24870.herokuapp.com/"
    live ="https://github.com/mengyue-z/Online-Offline-Budget-Trackers"
/></Col>
      <Col>
<Project 
    img="https://github.com/mengyue-z/weather-dashboard/raw/main/screenshots/img2.jpg"
    title="Weather Dashboard"
    description="This is an application that users can get weather information for different cities all over the world.
Once users search for a city, the current weather and 5-day forecast will be displayed."
live="https://mengyue-z.github.io/weather-dashboard/"
repo="https://github.com/mengyue-z/weather-dashboard"
/></Col>
<Col>
<Project 
    img="https://github.com/mengyue-z/Note-Taker/raw/main/public/assets/screenshot.jpg"
    title="Note Taker"
    description="This is a note-taking application powered by Express.js that users can write and save notes on the page and retrieve notes any time they want."
    repo="https://github.com/mengyue-z/Note-Taker"
    live ="https://vast-basin-31119.herokuapp.com/"
/></Col>
<Col>
<Project 
    img="https://github.com/mengyue-z/Project_Management_App/raw/main/screenshots/employee.png"
    title="Sprinter"
    description="Sprinter is an application for tracking and managing developer sprints.
    It is designed with you and your development sprints in mind. Use the app to add sprints, add employees and managers to sprints, and keep track of your progress and division of labor as your project progresses."
    repo="https://github.com/mengyue-z/Project_Management_App"
    live ="https://fast-everglades-95030.herokuapp.com/"


/></Col>
</Row>
  );
}

export default Portfolio;
